WP-Authorinfo widget

Author: S.AKYUREK
Author URL: http://www.seyhunakyurek.com
Tags: about me, widget, biography, bio, author
Tested up to: 2.8 

-- Description --
Widget that adds author information box with social bookmarking links to your sidebar
Simply add your name, info, gravatar settings and social networks, this widget will creates a slick author information (bio) on your sidebar. Fully customizable and themeable.

Currently, the following socialnetworks are supported: 
 
* Delicious 
* Facebook 
* Friendfeed 
* Twitter 
* Linkedin
* Xing
* Youtube
* Technorati 
* Stumbleupon
* Feedburner 

-- Installation --

To install and configure: 
 
1. Download and extract WP-Authorinfo to your plugins folder.
2. Go to Administration panel > Plugins page and activate it.
3. Go to Administration panel > Themes > Widget page and add WP-MyBio to your sidebar and configure it.
4. No more steps, Its ready.

